Perl Wrapper for Video 4 Linux 2
CSCI 485 (SCADA Systems)
Vancouver Island University
Casey Yardley

Provides a perl wrapper for low level V4L2 interface.


Requirements
-swig2.0
-libv4l-dev
-libgtk2.0-dev

Edit Makefile to point to Video 4 Linux headers (defaults to x86_64)

Source Files
-grab.c and svv.c are C are examples of C applications using V4L2
-grab.pl is an implementation of grab.c using this wrapper
-libs contains relevant library header files
-V4L2.c contains some higher level V4L2 functions
-V4L2.i is the swig interface file
-WebCam.pm uses this wrapper to provide functions for acessing a webcam with Perl

Output
V4l2.so and V4l2.pm
